commit 75346cde7504efce1e43a86d67d432ace246df3e
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Apr 21 01:23:19 2009 -0700

    Install all cola resources into /usr/share/git-cola
    
    Debian bug #519972 suggested installing all items into
    /usr/share/git-cola/* instead of /usr/share/cola.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

