commit a3a86efe2db2ad029fdbfbacac24abde716f00fe (tag: refs/tags/v1.3.6)
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Mar 19 01:44:10 2009 -0700

    ui: simplify the log display by removing the search functionality
    
    This makes things the interface simpler by removing the rarely-used
    search feature in the cola log gui.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 7f714dc6b22ff4997ddbf1ab878e4eae0d107107
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 18 03:57:04 2009 -0700

    logging: add support for the cola.showoutput configuration variable
    
    This makes it so that the log window honors cola.showoutput.
    
        never = never show output
        always = always show the output
        errors = only show output on errors (default)
    
    This was done by centralizing logging logic in qtutils.log() and adding
    a model.should_display_log(status) method.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit e99440d6457809b03394099dd37c3ee579507c4d
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 18 03:53:28 2009 -0700

    ui: removed the status bar and cleaned out some dead code
    
    The status bar isn't very useful now that the right-hand tree widget
    succinctly displays a file's status, so remove it.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 312a5a416a499911d05e599607d7ccaae8616187
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Mar 14 03:49:41 2009 -0700

    gui: improve logging by adding drawers to the main window
    
    The log window is now a drawer positioned at the bottom of the
    main window.  This does away with the dreaded log window.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 2d7934c68cbfe78a3bef97107975c4581f061214
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 18 00:40:45 2009 -0700

    refactor: move log, options, and select commits into separate controllers
    
    This makes the util controller more lightweight separating out the
    logger, options, and select_commits functionality into separate
    controllers.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 362cc1b8f5f557e62d9fe9b844a6accecc859f8a
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Mar 18 00:38:59 2009 -0700

    qtutils: minimize the number of imports
    
    We now access QtGui classes through the QtGui module so that
    we import less and are more explicit about our module
    dependencies at the call sites.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 308e1d443d206db4d5cbde5a6e94f77dd78cd988
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Mar 19 01:48:41 2009 -0700

    refactor: avoid importing encode and decode directly
    
    This changes call sites so that they always use core.encode/decode
    instead of importing those functions directly.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit e02484f060b4ff112e64a51836c14661eec28c9d
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 17 22:00:44 2009 -0700

    json: run dos2unix on cola's pickle module
    
    This keeps jsonpickle consistent with the rest of cola.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 61cff60a6970afbed3c3cd3922303b18edb891a8
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 17 01:03:41 2009 -0700

    json: make cola's pickle module exception-safe
    
    cola.jsonpickle wasn't exception-safe and was breaking
    help('modules').
    
    This fixes Debian bug #519971.
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit fe010d0e298d2e6f989d5fabeffbb4712d41bf4c
