Date:   Sat Dec 27 00:41:00 2008 -0800

    win32: make gitk launch properly on win32
    
    Signed-off-by: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>

commit 52a0d1fd074929967f21241a36e87dd79ddb6006
