commit a542351b8d6ff7655346ef458c2f296543fd7ff5
Author: David Aguilar <davvid@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Dec 26 17:04:29 2008 -0800

    views: make all dialogs maximizable
    
    Windows requires that we use setWindowFlags on all dialogs
    otherwise Qt drops the maximize button.
    
